        <h2>Chevrolet</h2>
        <p>Chevrolet is an American automobile division of the American manufacturer General Motors (GM). Louis Chevrolet and ousted General Motors founder William C. Durant started the company on November 3, 1911, as the Chevrolet Motor Car Company.</p>
        <p><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Chevrolet offers a wide range of vehicles from compact cars to trucks and SUVs, known for their reliability and affordability.</p>
