    <div class="content">
        <h2>Bugatti</h2>
        <p>Bugatti Automobiles S.A.S. is a French high-performance luxury automobiles manufacturer and a subsidiary of Volkswagen AG. Bugatti was founded in 1909 in the then-German city of Molsheim, Alsace by Italian-born Ettore Bugatti.</p>
        <p><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Bugatti is synonymous with exclusivity, luxury, and unrivaled performance. Owning a Bugatti is a symbol of automotive excellence and prestige.</p>
